Name: Strength
Description: Affects physical damage dealt by gladiator's arms, marauder's arms, dark knight's arms, gunbreaker's arms, pugilist's arms, lancer's arms, samurai's arms, reaper's arms, thaumaturge's arms, arcanist's arms, red mage's arms, pictomancer's arms, conjurer's arms, astrologian's arms, sage's arms, and blue mage's arms.

Name: Dexterity
Description: Affects physical damage dealt by rogue's arms, viper's arms, archer's arms, machinist's arms, and dancer's arms.

Name: Vitality
Description: Affects maximum HP.

Name: Intelligence
Description: Affects attack magic potency when role is DPS.

Name: Mind
Description: Affects healing magic potency. Also affects attack magic potency when role is Healer.

Name: Piety
Description: Affects MP regeneration. Regeneration rate is determined by piety. Only applicable when in battle and role is Healer.

Name: Tenacity
Description: Affects the amount of physical and magic damage dealt and received, as well as HP restored. The higher the value, the more damage dealt, the more HP restored, and the less damage taken. Only applicable when role is Tank.

Name: Attack Power
Description: Affects amount of damage dealt by physical attacks. The higher the value, the more damage dealt.

Name: Defense
Description: Affects the amount of damage taken by physical attacks. The higher the value, the less damage taken.

Name: Direct Hit Rate
Description: Affects the rate at which your physical and magic attacks land direct hits, dealing slightly more damage than normal hits. The higher the value, the higher the frequency with which your hits will be direct. Higher values will also result in greater damage for actions which guarantee direct hits.

Name: Magic Defense
Description: Affects the amount of damage taken by magic attacks. The higher the value, the less damage taken.

Name: Critical Hit
Description: Affects the amount of physical and magic damage dealt, as well as HP restored. The higher the value, the higher the frequency with which your hits will be critical/higher the potency of critical hits.

Name: Slashing Resistance
Description: Decreases damage done by slashing attacks.

Name: Piercing Resistance
Description: Decreases damage done by piercing attacks.

Name: Blunt Resistance
Description: Decreases damage done by blunt attacks.

Name: Attack Magic Potency
Description: Affects the amount of damage dealt by magic attacks.

Name: Healing Magic Potency
Description: Affects the amount of HP restored via healing magic.

Name: Fire Resistance
Description: Decreases fire-aspected damage.

Name: Ice Resistance
Description: Decreases ice-aspected damage.

Name: Wind Resistance
Description: Decreases wind-aspected damage.

Name: Earth Resistance
Description: Decreases earth-aspected damage.

Name: Lightning Resistance
Description: Decreases lightning-aspected damage.

Name: Water Resistance
Description: Decreases water-aspected damage.

Name: Determination
Description: Affects the amount of damage dealt by both physical and magic attacks, as well as the amount of HP restored by healing spells.

Name: Skill Speed
Description: Affects both the casting and recast timers, as well as the damage over time potency for weaponskills and auto-attacks. The higher the value, the shorter the timers/higher the potency.

Name: Spell Speed
Description: Affects both the casting and recast timers for spells. The higher the value, the shorter the timers. Also affects a spell's damage over time or healing over time potency.

Name: Morale
Description: In PvP, replaces physical and magical defense in determining damage inflicted by other players. Also influences the amount of damage dealt to other players.

Name: Slow Resistance
Description: Shortens the duration of slow.

Name: Silence Resistance
Description: Shortens the duration of silence.

Name: Blind Resistance
Description: Shortens the duration of blind.

Name: Poison Resistance
Description: Shortens the duration of poison.

Name: Stun Resistance
Description: Shortens the duration of stun.

Name: Sleep Resistance
Description: Shortens the duration of sleep.

Name: Bind Resistance
Description: Shortens the duration of bind.

Name: Heavy Resistance
Description: Shortens the duration of heavy.

Name: Craftsmanship
Description: Affects the amount of progress achieved in a single synthesis step.

Name: Control
Description: Affects the amount of quality improved in a single synthesis step.

Name: Gathering
Description: Affects the rate at which items are gathered.

Name: Perception
Description: Affects item yield when gathering as a botanist or miner, and the size of fish when fishing or spearfishing.
